==不變NKT(iNKT)細胞==
最廣爲人知的一類CD1d依賴性NKT細胞會表達一種不變[[T細胞受體|T細胞受體]]（TCR）α鏈。這類NKT細胞即1型NKT細胞，或稱不變NKT（iNKT）細胞。1型NKT細胞的顯著特徵是能迅速對危險信號和促炎細胞因子作出反應。

不變NKT細胞能識別由CD1d分子呈遞的脂質。CD1d分子是一類非多態性的抗原呈遞分子，與1類MHC相似。這類細胞在小鼠和人之間的進化保守。人體內高度保守的T細胞受體（T細胞受體）由Va24-Ja18和Vb11組成，與糖脂抗原專一結合<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title = Invariant natural killer T cells: an innate activation scheme linked to diverse effector functions|url = http://www.nature.com/nri/journal/v13/n2/full/nri3369.html|journal = Nature Reviews Immunology|date = 2013-02-01|issn = 1474-1733|pages = 101–117|volume = 13|issue = 2|doi = 10.1038/nri3369|language = en|first = Patrick J.|last = Brennan|first2 = Manfred|last2 = Brigl|first3 = Michael B.|last3 = Brenner|access-date = 2016-09-11|archive-date = 2019-10-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191018200850/https://www.nature.com/articles/nri3369|dead-url = no}}</ref>。1型NKT細胞最經典的抗原爲α-半乳糖酰基鞘氨醇（αGalCer），一類從深海海綿''Agelas Mauritanius''中提純的化學物質的人工合成形式<ref>{{Cite journal|title = CD1d-restricted and TCR-mediated activation of valpha14 NKT cells by glycosylceramides|url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9374463|journal = Science (New York, N.Y.)|date = 1997-11-28|issn = 0036-8075|pmid = 9374463|pages = 1626–1629|volume = 278|issue = 5343|first = T.|last = Kawano|first2 = J.|last2 = Cui|first3 = Y.|last3 = Koezuka|first4 = I.|last4 = Toura|first5 = Y.|last5 = Kaneko|first6 = K.|last6 = Motoki|first7 = H.|last7 = Ueno|first8 = R.|last8 = Nakagawa|first9 = H.|last9 = Sato|doi = 10.1126/science.278.5343.1626|access-date = 2016-09-11|archive-date = 2016-09-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160923014357/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9374463|dead-url = no}}</ref>。1型NKT細胞在胸腺中發育，成熟後會分散至外週。肝臟中的NKT細胞數目最多，胸腺、外週血、脾臟、骨髓，以及脂肪組織中亦有NKT細胞存在。與小鼠相比，人體內的1型NKT細胞較少，且循環系統中的1型NKT細胞數目波動較大<ref name=":0" />。

目前，主要有5種iNKT細胞。每類細胞在活化後可以產生不同種類的細胞因子。亞型iNKT1、iNKT2，以及iNKT17能反映一些[[輔助T細胞|輔助T細胞]]細胞因子的產生。另外，一些亞型可以發揮與濾泡輔助T細胞類似的功能以及I1-10依賴的調節功能<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Development of invariant natural killer T cells|url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26802287|journal = Current Opinion in Immunology|date = 2016-01-20|issn = 1879-0372|pmid = 26802287|pages = 68–74|volume = 39|doi = 10.1016/j.coi.2016.01.001|first = Laurent|last = Gapin|access-date = 2016-09-11|archive-date = 2019-02-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190217085911/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26802287|dead-url = no}}</ref>。活化的1型NKT細胞可以改變免疫應答的強度以及種類。他們能夠像[[樹突狀細胞|樹突狀細胞]]、[[中性粒細胞|中性粒細胞]]、[[淋巴細胞|淋巴細胞]]一樣與其他免疫細胞發生交叉交流<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Presumed guilty: natural killer T cell defects and human disease|url = http://www.nature.com/nri/journal/v11/n2/full/nri2904.html|journal = Nature Reviews Immunology|date = 2011-02-01|issn = 1474-1733|pages = 131–142|volume = 11|issue = 2|doi = 10.1038/nri2904|language = en|first = Stuart P.|last = Berzins|first2 = Mark J.|last2 = Smyth|first3 = Alan G.|last3 = Baxter|access-date = 2016-09-11|archive-date = 2019-10-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191018200849/https://www.nature.com/articles/nri2904|dead-url = no}}</ref>。當抗原與不變T細胞受體結合時，1型NKT細胞即會活化。1型NKT細胞亦可以通過細胞因子信號間接活化<ref name=":0" />。

儘管1型NKT細胞數目不多，它們獨一無二的性質使得它們成爲一類能影響免疫系統行爲的重要免疫系統調節細胞<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Invariant natural killer T cells as sensors and managers of inflammation|url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1471490612001470|journal = Trends in Immunology|date = 2013-02-01|pmc = 3615427|pmid = 23017731|pages = 50–58|volume = 34|issue = 2|doi = 10.1016/j.it.2012.08.009|first = Luc|last = Van Kaer|first2 = Vrajesh V.|last2 = Parekh|first3 = Lan|last3 = Wu|access-date = 2016-09-11|archive-date = 2017-04-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170405123419/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1471490612001470|dead-url = no}}</ref>。已證明NKT細胞與慢性炎症性疾病，如自體免疫病、哮喘，以及代謝綜合徵有關。在患有自體免疫病的人體內，外週血的1型NKT細胞數目下降。不過，目前尚不清楚這是病因還是症狀。實驗鼠早期發育過程中缺乏微生物的接觸可導致1型NKT細胞數目的上升以及免疫疾病的發生<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Microbial Exposure During Early Life Has Persistent Effects on Natural Killer T Cell Function|journal = Science (New York, N.Y.)|date = 2012-04-27|issn = 0036-8075|pmc = 3437652|pmid = 22442383|pages = 489–493|volume = 336|issue = 6080|doi = 10.1126/science.1219328|first = Torsten|last = Olszak|first2 = Dingding|last2 = An|first3 = Sebastian|last3 = Zeissig|first4 = Miguel Pinilla|last4 = Vera|first5 = Julia|last5 = Richter|first6 = Andre|last6 = Franke|first7 = Jonathan N.|last7 = Glickman|first8 = Reiner|last8 = Siebert|first9 = Rebecca M.|last9 = Baron}}</ref>。

==功能==
活化後，NKT細胞可以產生大量的[[干擾素伽馬|干擾素-γ]]、[[白细胞介素-4|IL-4]]（白細胞介素4），以及[[粒细胞-巨噬细胞集落刺激因子|粒细胞-巨噬细胞集落刺激因子]]（granulocyte-macrophage colony-stimulating factor）。此外，NKT細胞還能產生一些[[細胞因子|細胞因子]]和[[趨化因子|趨化因子]]（如IL-2、IL-13、IL-17、IL-21、[[肿瘤坏死因子-α|肿瘤坏死因子-α]]）。

==意義==
NKT細胞對於[[免疫|免疫]]的一些功能的發揮是至關重要的。已證明NKT細胞的功能失調或欠缺可能會造成[[自體免疫病|自體免疫病]]（比如[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]和[[動脈粥樣硬化|動脈粥樣硬化]]）以及[[癌症|癌症]]。一些研究表明，NKT細胞與人類哮喘的發病也有一定聯繫<ref>Cromie, William J. [http://www.news.harvard.edu/gazette/2006/03.16/01-asthma.html Researchers uncover cause of asthma] {{Wayback|url=http://www.news.harvard.edu/gazette/2006/03.16/01-asthma.html |date=20060405004234 }} Harvard University Gazette, March 16, 2006.</ref>。

NKT細胞的對細胞因子（如IL-2、IFN-γ、TNF-α、IL4）的快速釋放可能有臨床上的應用價值，因爲這些因子能促進或抑制不同的免疫反應。

目前，大量關於NKT細胞的臨床實驗都是用[[細胞因子誘導的殺傷細胞|細胞因子誘導的殺傷細胞]]（cytokine-induced killer cell, CIK）進行的<ref>Schmeel LC, Schmeel FC, Coch C, Schmidt-Wolf IG. [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25381063 Cytokine-induced killer cell (CIK) in cancer immunotherapy: report of the international registry on CIK cells (IRCC)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25381063 |date=20170319112720 }}. J Cancer Res Clin Oncol. 2014 Nov 8. [[Digital_object_identifier|doi]]:[http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s00432-014-1864-3 10.1007/s00432-014-1864-3]. [[PubMed_Identifier|PMID]] [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25381063 25381063] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25381063 |date=20170319112720 }}</ref>。

